## Section 0 — Intro

IMG-00-01 [TITLE]: Lagoon at dawn, boat nearing the Arsenal water gate, high brick walls, stone arch over dark water, two guards in archway, robed figure with satchel in a second boat, cold grey-blue light
IMG-00-02 [TITLE]: Brick-vaulted scribes' room, clerk in dark robes opening a register at wooden table, grey morning window light, smaller volume beside, oil lamp on iron stand, warm amber and cool grey
IMG-00-03: Arsenal courtyard at dawn, workers in tunics crossing stone yard toward workshops, foreman by wooden notice board, scribe comparing document against it, grey November light, distant forge smoke, muted grey-blue and ochre

