## Section 6 — Outro

IMG-06-01: Stone corridor of a government building, young clerk carrying sealed register toward door at far end, cold stone floor, sconce lamp at midpoint, door ajar with warm light through it, rest in cool shadow, grey corridor with warm distant door-light
IMG-06-02 [TITLE]: Register lying open on stone, deep ochre pages, faded sepia ink, certification page with four signatures and wax seal, cracked binding, grey archival light from above, no figures
IMG-06-03: Scribes' room in December, scribe drafting letter by lamplight, three documents with broken seals beside register, partially written response on table, window showing grey winter light, warm amber lamp and cool grey-blue winter atmosphere
